#: src/application.rs
msgid ""
"FolderPlay is a minimalist music player developed in Rust and GTK4. Its "
"philosophy is simple: letting you enjoy your local collection by faithfully "
"respecting your disk's folder structure—it doesn't group by artist, "
"album, or genre. It simply respects your order."
msgstr ""

#: src/application.rs
msgid "Designed with a strong focus on Lossless Hi-Res audio playback."
msgstr ""

#: src/preferences.rs
msgid "Audio Output"
msgstr ""

#: src/preferences.rs
msgid ""
"HiFi sends audio directly to your DAC without resampling. Standard uses "
"PulseAudio for maximum compatibility."
msgstr ""

#: src/preferences.rs
msgid "Output"
msgstr ""

#: src/preferences.rs
msgid "Automatic"
msgstr ""

#: src/preferences.rs
msgid "HiFi (Bit-perfect)"
